description:
The Mutuals Public Register is the public record of registered mutual societies:

* building societies
* credit unions
* friendly societies
* registered societies

It contains:

* details of societies’ registered offices and contact information
the services they offer
* public documents such as yearly returns and accounts
licenseDetails: Copyright information on the site places restrictions on re-use.
name: Mutuals Public Register
onlineAccessDetails: It is possible to search the register online, but documents and bulk download of data are not freely available.
